{
  "texts": [
    "The small parameter size and simple training procedure of RC together lead to much less training time and resource consumption.",
    "As the capacity of deep learning increases, the parameter size also grows, which is a challenge for practical application.",
    "For example, the memory of smart watch is around typically 2GB, so it can be equipped with GPT (~0.5 GB) or BERT-Large (~1.3 GB).",
    "For large networks such as GPT3 (~652 GB) and GPT4 (~6557 GB), only workstations or high performance cluster (HPC) can incorporate them.",
    "Inversely, since RC has much less parameters, it can be applied on diverse devices flexibly."
  ]
}